WEBVTT

00:00:00.856 --> 00:00:03.190
I want to introduce you
to an amazing woman.

00:00:03.690 --> 00:00:05.698
Her name is Davinia.

00:00:06.444 --> 00:00:10.849
Davinia was born in Jamaica,
emigrated to the US at the age of 18,

00:00:10.873 --> 00:00:13.604
and now lives just outside
of Washington, DC.

00:00:14.262 --> 00:00:17.064
She's not a high-powered
political staffer,

00:00:17.088 --> 00:00:18.261
nor a lobbyist.

00:00:18.676 --> 00:00:21.605
She'd probably tell you
she's quite unremarkable,

00:00:21.629 --> 00:00:24.154
but she's having
the most remarkable impact.

00:00:24.471 --> 00:00:25.991
What's incredible about Davinia

00:00:26.015 --> 00:00:28.878
is that she's willing to spend
time every single week

00:00:28.902 --> 00:00:31.307
focused on people who are not her: